msgid "HELP_TASKS"
msgstr ""
"You need to do tasks.\n"
"Some tasks require to come close to the subject of testing (812, partly 938).\n"
"Some tasks require to bring Class-D (162, 173, 266, 522, 939, partly 938).\n"
"Some tasks require to bring something to special place (347, 914).\n"
"Some tasks require to come with special item (791).\n"
"Some tasks require to interact or use subject of testing (023, 067)."

msgid "HELP_EVENTS"
msgstr ""
"Also the game has events.\n"
"There are only three events implemented right now - Chaos Insurgency invasion, SCP-023 critical state and SCP-347 containment breach.\n"
"For the first one, you need to call MTF (maybe more then one time), just when they appear.\n"
"For SCP-023 - if you round took long (> 2 minutes), you need to go to Maintenance Zone and go to SCP-023, replacing his \"eyes\" as soon, as possible.\n"
"For the later one you need to catch SCP-347 (which was not detected before) as soon as possible\n"
"(She is marked by the red radar, because this woman is invisible)."

